parameters: Senpai♪ Do you have some free time after this?

No, just♪ If it's okay with you, would you like to join us
for a drinking party?
Your husband only comes home on weekends, right, Senpai?
Well... I don't mind a drinking party but...

I don't think it'll be very lively with someone like me
there, you know?

It might create a weird atmosphere if a married person mixes
in with the younger crowd...

It might be a problem with the section chief or the
department head, but it's totally fine with you, Senpai♪

Plus, you're popular among the men in the company, so I
think everyone would be happy♪
It's nice to hear that, but...

We've made a reservation at a pub near the station, so
please come over once you're done with work♪
It's Friday, so I have to go pick up Takkun...
Mmm... I have to contact Takkun...

Momone-chan... Are you in the middle of any urgent work
right now?

No... I don't have any urgent tasks assigned to me at the
moment...

Well... I have a bit of a different task I'd like to ask you
to do...
If it's cleaning, I'm good at it, so please leave it to me♪

It's not exactly cleaning... Ah... well... It's not not
cleaning either...
Hmm... So what kind of task is it?
I'd like you to entertain a client.

Entertaining is fine, but... is it okay for me, an office
worker, to do it?

No, no♪ You have a good reputation within the company♪ Could
you please do it for me?

If you insist that much, I can't refuse... If I'm suitable,
then I'll do it.

So... So you will! That's our Momone-chan! I'm definitely
counting on you!
So... When will the client be arriving here?
Actually, they're already in the president's office...
Ah, wait! Please wait! I'm not mentally prepared yet!!
Hohou... She's the one you were talking about earlier...

Exactly... She is our company's pride in accounting... no...
she belongs to the hospitality department, Momone-chan...

Ho... Hospitality department? What are you talking about! We
don't have such a department in our company!

Well... Our company has some departments that aren't
publicly disclosed...

That doesn't matter♪ If she's going to entertain us, then I
might consider that proposal...
Come on! Momone-chan! Please entertain our guest!
Eh!? What!? What should I do for entertainment...

You know what to do without me saying, right? I'll be
outside until the entertainment is over♪
Please! This job is critical for our company's future!
Eh? Uh... umm...! I'm really troubled if you say that!!
Feh!? Why are you getting naked!? What!?
Why, you ask... because this is hospitality♪

However... I must say I'm envious that you have an employee
like you♪

How about it? If you're willing, would you consider coming
to our company with better terms?

I'm flattered by the offer, but... I'm accustomed to where I
am now...
And I have a husband as well...

Well... I don't expect you to decide right now, but if you
ever find yourself in trouble, contact me immediately♪

No... I'm sorry for interrupting your work and making you
entertain.
I'll leave this matter in your hands then♪
Ye... Yes!! I'll do my best!

Ah...! You saved us, Momone-kun! Thanks to you, we didn't
miss out on a big deal!

I'll make sure to report this to the higher-ups, so you can
look forward to your bonus evaluation♪
If anything comes up again, I'll be counting on you!
If there is, that is♪ If there is♪

I'm sorry for giving you different work, feel free to return
to your usual duties♪
Geez... this kind of work is harder than my regular job...

I have to keep this a secret from Takkun that I did this
kind of work...
This store sells all sorts of things...
They even have a full range of party goods...
Ehehe♪ I get so excited in shops like this♪
I wonder if this outfit is some kind of cosplay costume...
A kitty cat cosplay outfit might be a bit cute♪

I wonder if Tak-kun would be surprised if I greeted him
wearing this outfit...
Sorry! It took me a bit longer to change!

It's okay♪ I haven't been waiting long, and I just came out
too♪

More importantly... the public pool was farther away than I
thought...
But we made it without getting lost, so that's good♪

Tsk tsk tsk... You can't rush when you're in front of the
pool
There's something we have to do first, right?
Of course there is～... Warm-up exercises～
Ah... now that you mention it, that's right...

I completely forgot♪ Well then, let's do the warm-up
exercises...
Eh? What's up? Aren't we going to do the warm-up exercises?
We are, but come over here♪
Momone...? What are you planning to do in a place like this?
Laying out the vinyl sheet on the ground...
Now♪ Let's start the warm-up exercises♪

While looking at the kitty costume, I accidentally slipped
into some weird fantasies...

Takkun isn't a pervert who would make his bride wear erotic
outfits and take her for a walk!!
Uuu!! I won't lose to such desires!!
But I'm gonna buy it anyway~♪
Momone-senpai, is something wrong? Do you have any concerns?

Ye... Yes... I made a mistake at work... and now there's a
claim from a customer...
I see... Your department must be tough, Kanae-chan.
Momone-senpai!! Please, I beg you! Can you help me!?
I'm... not good at dealing with customer claims...
What!? Me!? No... I can't do that!
I specialize in desk work... I can't handle claims...

Please!! It's a lifetime request! Could you handle it
instead of me?

Look... If it's you, senpai, with your gentle manner, I
don't think the customer would get angry...
I don't think that's the case though...
Kanae-san... the customer is calling for you?
What!? Ah... yes! I'll be right there!!
Ahhhn!! Senpai!! Please, I'm begging youuu!!
Mmm... Can't be helped... Just this once, okay?

Sorry to keep you waiting... On behalf of Katou, I, Onodera,
will take care of...

You've caused me losses and made me wait, what an outrageous
company!!

And to think you're trying to deceive me by changing the
person in charge, that's absolutely unacceptable!!
I'm terribly sorry for the inconvenience Katou has caused...

It's more than just an inconvenience!! You will take
responsibility for this!
Hurry up and show your butt!!

Hurry up!! I'm busy! I don't have time to waste in a place
like this!!
If you're truly sorry, then hurry up and show your butt!!

If you really mean to apologize, then showing your butt
should be no problem!

Anyway, my fury has been calmed by your apology. Let's
accept the apology and let bygones be bygones♪

You should go to the bathroom quickly and wash away the
filth of society♪
Then I shall entrust you with work from now on as well.
Well then, I shall take my leave♪
What's wrong? You suddenly started grinning...

Kanae-chan said she would take over the complaint handling
for me...
That's right!! I'll be the one to handle the complaint!
Complaint handling? I didn't say anything like that.
I just came to bring the expense documents...
Eh!? Documents!? There wasn't a complaint from a customer?
Senpai, that's terrible♪ I wouldn't make such a mistake♪
Maybe you should take a break? You work too hard, Senpai♪
Ah... Ahaha... Yeah, maybe you're right...
Please go over the documents then♪ Thank you♪
Sigh... That was just a dream...
Yeah, right... Handling a complaint with my butt...
What am I thinking... I should go home early today...
Hmm? This is a school classroom, isn't it...
It kind of makes me reminisce about my school days♪
Since I'm here, I might as well take a little peek♪

Hmm... There's no one inside, so maybe they're doing PE in
the schoolyard...
Huh? What's that? It looks like someone's in the back...
Hmm... They're talking, so maybe there are two people...

Ah!! Could it be... a couple that skipped class to get all
lovey-dovey...
Ahhn! It's wrong to peek out of mere curiosity!

It's a page of their youth! Peeking at such precious
memories...
But... maybe just a little peek wouldn't hurt...
No way! Momone!! Peeping is a crime!!
Ahhn! But I want to see!!
That's right!! Just the tip is okay, right?♪
I'll just take a little peek♪

You're going to pay for these ripped tights and the extra,
you know!
Sorry♪ Like I said before, I'll pay for it, so don't worry♪

Just to confirm, you're not going to pay with dirty bills,
right?

Of course not♪ I'll pay with different money than what I
used to wipe my butt♪
Ah... Akane, what are you doing?!!
Ahhn! I have to go out there and warn them right now!!

If they find out I sneaked in, they'll think I'm the
pervert...

Sigh... I feel like I've witnessed an incredible page of
youth...
